  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/imagecapturecore\/icscannermeasurementunit\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T16:16:27Z\n---\n\n# ICScannerMeasurementUnit\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nThe unit of measurement used by the scanner.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum ICScannerMeasurementUnit\n```\n\n## Overview\n\nThe values correspond to the `ICAP_UNITS` values as defined in the `TWAIN` Specification.\n\n## Constants\n\n- **ICScannerMeasurementUnit.centimeters**\n- **ICScannerMeasurementUnit.inches**\n- **ICScannerMeasurementUnit.picas**\n- **ICScannerMeasurementUnit.pixels**\n- **ICScannerMeasurementUnit.points**\n- **ICScannerMeasurementUnit.twips**\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Document Sizes\n\n- **ICScannerDocumentType**: The supported document size types.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
